          <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question"><span data-i18n="faq.q4_2">Do you offer quality guarantees?</span><svg class="faq-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg></div><div class="faq-answer" data-i18n="faq.a4_2">Yes! 100% quality guarantee. Defective products will be replaced or refunded.</div></div>
